section(class="template-wrapper")
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")
    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")

            div(class="row")
                h5(class="ta-c") #[strong.u-textColor_4 1. ] Read the article. Complete it with the correct form of the verbs.
                div(class="row-flex")
                    div(class="col-flex-sm12 col-flex-md12 col-center")
                        div(class="row")
                            h2(class="ta-c") OPENING GAME AT THE ALL NEW NATIONAL BALLPARK

                            p(class="mt60")
                                | No one wanted to miss
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_1" name="tfInputRadio_1" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_1" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") watching
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_2" name="tfInputRadio_1" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_2" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to watch
                                | the opening game at the all new and renovated National BallPark. Fans didn’t mind
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_3" name="tfInputRadio_2" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_3" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") waiting
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_4" name="tfInputRadio_2" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_4" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to wait
                                | in line to buy the last few tickets for sale. Fans enjoyed
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_5" name="tfInputRadio_3" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_5" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") looking at
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_6" name="tfInputRadio_3" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_6" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to look at
                                | the new statue of their local team´s star player that is now displayed at the entrance of the park.
                            p
                                | The local team's star player was standing on the pitcher's mound getting ready
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_7" name="tfInputRadio_4" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_7" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") throwing
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_8" name="tfInputRadio_4" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_8" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to throw
                                | the first pitch. He was probably remembering
                                span(class="c-textField")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_9" name="tfInputRadio_5" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_9" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") hitting
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_10" name="tfInputRadio_5" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_10" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to hit
                                | home runs he hit in the old park. Several people mentioned
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_11" name="tfInputRadio_6" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_11" class="c-CheckSelected mt10 ml10 mr10") missing
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_12" name="tfInputRadio_6" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_12" class="c-CheckSelected mt10 ml10 mr10") to miss
                                | the old park, but not the cold weather conditions there. The renovated park offers fans better shelter to changing weather conditions.

                            p
                                | A new train line was also recently inaugurated to offer fans a public transportation alternative to get to the park. Most people decided
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_13" name="tfInputRadio_7" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_13" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") taking
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_14" name="tfInputRadio_7" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_14" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to take
                                | this new train line to the game. Some people admitted
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_15" name="tfInputRadio_8" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_15" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") liking
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_16" name="tfInputRadio_8" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_16" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to like
                                | the experience, but others complained about how crowded the line was. Others risked
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_17" name="tfInputRadio_9" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_17" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") driving
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_18" name="tfInputRadio_9" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_18" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to drive
                                | and later found it difficult to park. The train company regretted not
                                span(class="c-textField ml10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_19" name="tfInputRadio_10" value="1")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_19" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") planning
                                span(class="c-textField mr10")
                                    input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="inputRadio_20" name="tfInputRadio_10" value="2")
                                    label(for="inputRadio_20" class="c-CheckSelected ml10 mr10") to plan
                                | for the large number of fans who wanted to take the train.

    |
